title: 351 - The Cowboy Rulebook
description: Mitch Hurwitz is back! Mitch and Dan talk Arrested Development, Golden Girls, upcoming projects and the future of network TV. Singer/songwriter Robbie Fulks joins in with some tales told via country music. Featuring Dan Harmon, Jeff Bryan Davis, Mitch Hurwitz, Robbie Fulks and Rob Schrab.
